com.vdisk.net

接口 VDiskAPI.UploadRequest

  • 所有已知实现类:
    VDiskAPI.BasicUploadRequest, VDiskAPI.ComplexUploadRequest
    封闭类:
    VDiskAPI<SESS_T extends Session>

    public static interface VDiskAPI.UploadRequest
    A request to upload a file to VDisk. This request can be canceled by calling abort().

    • 方法概要

      方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      void abort()
      Aborts the request.
      VDiskAPI.Entry upload()
      Executes the request.

    • 方法详细资料

      • abort

        void abort()
        Aborts the request. The original call to upload() will throw a VDiskPartialFileException.

      • upload

        VDiskAPI.Entry upload()
                      throws VDiskException
        Executes the request.
        返回:
        an VDiskAPI.Entry representing the uploaded file.
        抛出:
        VDiskPartialFileException - if the request was canceled before completion.
        VDiskServerException - if the server responds with an error code. See the constants in VDiskServerException for the meaning of each error code. The most common error codes you can expect from this call are 404 (path to upload not found), 507 (user over quota), and 400 (unexpected parent rev).
        VDiskIOException - if any network-related error occurs.
        VDiskException - for any other unknown errors. This is also a superclass of all other VDisk exceptions, so you may want to only catch this exception which signals that some kind of error occurred.
